OL,4,Cat sea, migrant tells court
OL,6,FAn asylum seeker on board a dinghy
OL,7,Fwhen four others drowned in the
OL,8,FEnglish Channel has told a court that
OL,9,Fif it was not for the driver "we would
OL,10,Fhave all died".
OL,12,FAmrullah Ahmadzai, from Afghanistan,
OL,13,Fdescribed how everyone was screaming
OL,14,Fand trying to call for help on their
OL,15,Fmobile phones during a journey in an
OL,16,Finflatable vessel, before being
OL,17,Frescued by a fishing boat.
