OL,3,CWithout pilot 'we would have all died'
OL,4,Cat sea, migrant tells court
OL,6,FIbrahima Bah, who is believed to have
OL,7,Fpiloted the boat, is on trial for
OL,8,Fmanslaughter of the four migrants who
OL,9,Fdied while seeking passage from France
OL,10,Fto the UK on December 14 2022.
OL,12,FJurors had heard the home-built, low-
OL,13,Fquality inflatable should have had no
OL,14,Fmore than 20 people on board, but in
OL,15,Ffact tried to carry at least 43 people
OL,16,Facross the English Channel that night.
