OL,3,CWithout pilot 'we would have all died'
OL,4,Cat sea, migrant tells court
OL,6,FAt Canterbury Crown Court on Wednesday
OL,7,F(31 January), Mr Ahmadzai recalled the
OL,8,Fboat getting into trouble after about
OL,9,Fan hour on the sea, with water filling
OL,10,Fup the boat reaching above his knees.
OL,12,FHe described how the skipper tried to
OL,13,Fsteer the dinghy towards a fishing
OL,14,Fboat to help the passengers.
OL,16,FMr Ahmadzai said: "I could see he was
OL,17,Fdriving towards the fishing boat but
OL,18,Fat the same time he was shouting at
OL,19,Feveryone 'calm down, I'm going to take
OL,20,Fyou there' but no-one was listening to
OL,21,Fhim.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
