OL,3,CWithout pilot 'we would have all died'
OL,4,Cat sea, migrant tells court
OL,6,F"It's not his fault, he was trying his
OL,7,Fbest... they were all scared and
OL,8,Fscreaming and they all stood up
OL,9,Fsuddenly."
OL,11,FHe added: "It was because of this
OL,12,Fdriver who played a big part in our
OL,13,Flives that took us closer to the
OL,14,Ffishing boat.
OL,16,F"If it wasn't for him we would have
OL,17,Fall died."
