OL,3,CWithout pilot 'we would have all died'
OL,4,Cat sea, migrant tells court
OL,6,FMr Ahmadzai said that when the fellow
OL,7,Fmigrants in the boat stood up the
OL,8,Fwater rose more and the boarded floor
OL,9,Fwent down, leading to people getting
OL,10,Finto the water or stuck in the middle
OL,11,Fof the boat.
OL,13,FAnother witness, Ghanam Gul Ahmadzai,
OL,14,Fon the boat that night, described how
OL,15,Fthe wooden floor "burst" underneath as
OL,16,Fthey got closer to the fishing boat.
