OL,3,CWithout pilot 'we would have all died'
OL,4,Cat sea, migrant tells court
OL,6,FHe said: "We all fell into the water,
OL,7,Fall the boys, some of them were
OL,8,Fhanging on to the remains of the boat
OL,9,Fwe were actually travelling in, some
OL,10,Fof them were actually in the water."
OL,12,FProsecutor Duncan Atkinson had told
OL,13,Fjurors Bah, who is over 18, owed his
OL,14,Ffellow passengers a "duty of care" by
OL,15,Fbeing the pilot, but he was not
OL,16,Ftrained or licensed to steer the
OL,17,Fdinghy, and was aware it was
OL,18,Fovercrowded and lacked safety
OL,19,Fequipment.
