OL,4,Cat sea, migrant tells court
OL,6,FThe court heard from witnesses that
OL,7,Fbefore the voyage the group of
OL,8,Fmigrants were transported in three
OL,9,Fcars to the shoreline, organised by
OL,10,FKurdish agents.
OL,12,FThe smugglers also brought the boat in
OL,13,Fa car, and got the passengers to help
OL,14,Fpump it up.
OL,16,FMr Ahmadzai said: "During that time
OL,17,Fthey were very cruel to migrants. They
OL,18,Fforced them and sometimes they beat
OL,19,Fthem to pump the dinghy.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
