OL,3,CWithout pilot 'we would have all died'
OL,4,Cat sea, migrant tells court
OL,6,F"The reason they are cruel (is)
OL,7,Fthey're worried and scared the police
OL,8,Fmight come and send us back, so that's
OL,9,Fwhy they're in a rush."
OL,11,FMr Gul Ahmadzai, who is also from
OL,12,FAfghanistan, said the boat was then
OL,13,Fput into the water and the migrants
OL,14,Fjumped into the boat from the sea.
OL,16,FHe described how before the boat
OL,17,F"ripped apart" that it started to fill
OL,18,Fwith water slowly and then gradually
OL,19,Fincreased to under his knee in the
OL,20,Fboat.
