OL,3,CWithout pilot 'we would have all died'
OL,4,Cat sea, migrant tells court
OL,6,FHe added there was one person with a
OL,7,Fbucket with him "throwing water back
OL,8,Finto the sea".
OL,10,FBah, who is also accused of
OL,11,Ffacilitating a breach of immigration
OL,12,Flaw, denies all charges.
OL,14,FOn Monday (29 January), jurors heard
OL,15,Fthat Bah's defence is likely to be
OL,16,Fthat he was acting under duress and
OL,17,Fthat he did not know he was
OL,18,Ffacilitating a breach of immigration
OL,19,Flaw.
OL,21,FThe trial continues.
